cosmic-order (0.16.0) noble; urgency=medium

  * Screensaver: default terminal switched to Alacritty, which self-fullscreens
    via startup_mode=Fullscreen (avoids the cosmic-term fullscreen freeze).
  * Screensaver: power-aware effect profiles are now applied at runtime
    (Full/Standard/Simple/Minimal tiers, selected from EFFECT_PROFILE).
  * Screensaver: fixed a password-prompt hang during mouse parking.
  * App: --page <visuals|tool-sync|screensaver> opens the GUI to a page.
  * App: window title now reads "COSMIC ORDER".
  * Packaging: declare runtime deps — Recommends alacritty, swayidle; Suggests
    figlet, ydotool.
  * Removed: caffeine / idle-inhibitor feature (use systemd-inhibit instead).
  * Tooling: scripts/vm-test.sh + `just vm-test` (build/deploy/screenshot on a VM).

 -- Jonathan Freed <jon@freed-dev.com>  Fri, 22 May 2026 12:00:00 -0400

cosmic-order (0.15.0) noble; urgency=medium

  * Visuals: COSMIC built-in themes selector (Dark/Light/HC variants).
  * Screensaver: power settings section with live D-Bus state and
    per-profile effect overrides.
  * Screensaver: clock font input.
  * Screensaver: warn when bundled shell scripts are not installed.
  * Wallpaper: cosmic-order wallpaper add --set applies the image.
  * Tool sync: configurable Neovim colorscheme (default tokyonight).
  * Tool sync: surface manual-reload hints for Zellij, fzf, lazygit.
  * Theme: high-contrast variants apply via CosmicTheme::write_entry.
  * Window size persists across sessions.

 -- Jonathan Freed <jon@freed-dev.com>  Sun, 10 May 2026 12:00:00 -0400

